    "Mökander, et al. [115] put forth a multi-tiered strategy consisting of three layers: governance audits, which scrutinize technology providers responsible for designing and distributing LLMs; model audits, which evaluate LLMs following pre-training but before they are deployed; and application audits, which assess applications that utilize LLMs."
